nodes.text: Gujdim Wiphshun was a male Gran who served as governor of the Gran Protectorate on Malastare.

In 32 BBY, Gujdim Wiphshun hosted peace-talks between the Lannik High Court and the Red Iaro terrorists. The peace talks were held in the presence of the Gran Protectorate. Later, a group of Jedi who were also present during the interviews and acted as arbitrators.
